## 5. raw#10 honest C3

1. **Elevidys 2023→2024 expansion** = first FDA AAV5 micro-dystrophin gene therapy DMD. 4-5세 initial → 2024 expansion 4세+. SRP-9001 Sarepta. 양자-VQE 의 AAV5 capsid + immunogenicity 회피 fit.
2. **givinostat Duvyzat 2024** = first FDA HDAC pan-deacetylase DMD 6세+. EPIDYS Phase 3 trial. quantum-VQE 의 HDAC selectivity leverage (cross-cancer HDAC paradigm).
3. **vamorolone Agamree 2023** = first FDA novel corticosteroid-alternative DMD. dissociative GR ligand (transrepression preserved + transactivation 감소). PERSEUS 18-month phase 2/3. cross-osteoporosis_specific + pediatric_rare.
4. **eteplirsen + golodirsen + viltolarsen + casimersen 2016-2021** = exon-skipping ASO 4-drug paradigm. PMO (phosphorodiamidate morpholino oligomer) chemistry. dystrophin restoration <1% functional 이슈 + 기능적 임상 outcome 논쟁 ongoing.
5. **ataluren Translarna** = nonsense DMD 13% EU + 한국 conditional. US FDA 미승인 → 2024 EU withdrawn (CHMP negative opinion). ribosomal readthrough mechanism 의 임상 한계.
6. **prednisone + deflazacort (Emflaza) 2017** = 만성 corticosteroid 1L 표준 35+ year DMD. anti-inflammatory + muscle membrane stabilization. cushingoid + osteoporosis + 성장 지연 부작용 → vamorolone alternative emergence.
7. **pamrevlumab Phase 3 fail 2023** = anti-CTGF DMD paradigm lessons. fibrosis-axis 의 임상 한계. quantum-VQE 의 CTGF/CCN2 modeling 한정.
8. **ATSN-101 + LGMD2I AAV research (Atsena Therapeutics)** = LGMD subtype gene therapy. 30+ LGMD subtype 각각 별도 gene therapy 필요 — N-of-1 paradigm fit.
9. **viltolarsen (Viltepso) NS Pharma 한국** = exon 53 ASO. 한국 K-DMD 임상 framework + 산정특례 + DMD 환자 등록 cross-link.
10. **wet-lab + clinical RCT 없음** — quantum-only in-silico, muscular dystrophy specific 임상 의미 한정.

